      "span_text": "The transposon plasmid, pT2/shp53/GFP4, which encodes a short hairpin RNA against the tumor suppressor p53, with GFP as a reporter, was a gift from Dr. John Ohlfest and is referred to as pT2/shp53 [CITATION_2] ."
